This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image segmentation and object proposal generation. Additionally, the paper proposes a new algorithm for these tasks, which suggests that it may also belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the use of combinatorial grouping, which could place it in the Graphics (cs.GR) sub-category. Finally, the empirical validation conducted on various datasets suggests that it may also belong to the Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
